Sentencas: In this study, ultrafine Ce0.8Y0.2-xCaxO2-delta (x =0 to 0.1) powders have been successfully prepared by the sol-gel method.
Titulo: Synthesis and Characterization of Ce0.8Y0.2-xCaxO2-δ as Electrolyte for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The samples were characterized by TG-DSC, XRD and AC impedance.
Titulo: Synthesis and Characterization of Ce0.8Y0.2-xCaxO2-δ as Electrolyte for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Experimental results indicated that highly phase-pure cubic fluorite electrolyte Ce0.8Y0.2-xCaxO2-delta series electrolytes have higher relatively dense over 96% can obtained after sintered at 1400 degrees C, Among all the samples, Ce0.8Y0.1Ca0.1O1.85 shows excellent ionic conductivity of 0.041 S/cm measured at 800 degrees C and lower conductive activation energy 0.89 eV.
Titulo: Synthesis and Characterization of Ce0.8Y0.2-xCaxO2-δ as Electrolyte for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
